column2: SELECT   p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.z, s.tile, s.xFocal, s.yFocal, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, s.snMedian_u, s.snMedian_g, s.snMedian_r, s.snMedian_i, s.snMedian_z, s.ra, s.dec, s.cx, s.cy, s.cz, s.htmID,s.primTarget, s.secTarget,s.waveMin, s.waveMax, s.sciencePrimary, s.loadVersion, s.plateID, s.spectrographID, s.targetObjID, s.bestObjID, s.img, s.sourceType, s.targetType, s.fluxObjID, s.survey, s.class FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID  JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id
